reated a stand-off with ExxonMobil. ...</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=
=80=9CAdvising companies and their management teams is a core part of our b=
usiness, and we=E2=80=99re thrilled to have John Hess, a long-standing clie=
nt, join our board,=E2=80=9D the firm said in a statement.</p><p style=3D"m=
argin: 16px 0;">A senior Wall Street adviser said it was =E2=80=9Cvery rare=
