as a trusted adviser, expert in financial matters, who could give the compa=
ny=E2=80=99s managers good advice. Having her on the board would be valuabl=
e, and not a conflict of interest, because it=E2=80=99s not like the compan=
y was going around=C2=A0<em>bidding out=C2=A0</em>investment banking servic=
es. The company=E2=80=99s trusted investment banker would be on the board, =
and <em>other=C2=A0</em>investment bankers wouldn=E2=80=99t matter. Now of =
