=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CStress?=E2=80=9D =E2=80=9CP=
rocess?=E2=80=9D =E2=80=9CMake your Salesforce the best?=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</p>=
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Within an hour, the group=E2=80=94one of four =
teams spread out on the first two floors of Nashville=E2=80=99s Virgin Hote=
l=E2=80=94had written a twangy number about cloud software, complete with t=
