to criminal juries</a>, but if you are writing songs that are notionally ad=
dressed to potential clients,=C2=A0<em>shouldn=E2=80=99t you be singing the=
m to the clients? </em>Like you show up to pitch your software consulting s=
ervices and you burst into song? <em>That=C2=A0</em>is the corporate singin=
g I=E2=80=99d like to see. I guess <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbu=
